column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE BAR TIFFIN, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210627568
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, dried grapes, cocoa butter, vegetable fats (palm, shea), WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), cocoa mass, invert sugar syrup, emulsifiers (E442, E476, sunflower lecithin), tapioca starch, rapeseed oil, raising agents (E500, E503), salt, flavourings. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.COCOA SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 02/09/2017
